  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Grocery Store Simulator you take on the role of a grocery store manager. It's a first-person game where you handle every aspect of running a grocery business. From working the checkout to managing stock in the warehouse, each choice you make affects your store’s success. Play by yourself or with friends in online co-op mode to expand your store and improve your management skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1aa9f85f85b578af0df0b8c06a5274fe.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your store equipment anywhere you want, check out customer items, make sure your pricing is right, and keep shelves stocked to keep customers happy. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/e006f45b43bcaa7c34a475b74a8113d8.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with your friends online in a 4 player co-op mode to run your store together, sharing tasks and strategies to boost profits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/f91144be5889350a27ac3a9bcb919af1.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order new products, manage deliveries, and keep your warehouse organized to efficiently use the limited space and meet the daily needs of your store. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/46459d0bdd783005e91d0273093ec584.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your store with any wallpaper you choose and give it a unique and memorable name. You can also decorate your store however you want!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Grocery Store Simulator you take on the role of a grocery store manager. It's a first-person game where you handle every aspect of running a grocery business. From working the checkout to managing stock in the warehouse, each choice you make affects your store’s success. Play by yourself or with friends in online co-op mode to expand your store and improve your management skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1aa9f85f85b578af0df0b8c06a5274fe.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place your store equipment anywhere you want, check out customer items, make sure your pricing is right, and keep shelves stocked to keep customers happy. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/1dda61bfec3a36ae97abffd544a79192.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/e006f45b43bcaa7c34a475b74a8113d8.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with your friends online in a 4 player co-op mode to run your store together, sharing tasks and strategies to boost profits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/6739f483a6a623eeb05bfbcb831029fc.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/f91144be5889350a27ac3a9bcb919af1.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order new products, manage deliveries, and keep your warehouse organized to efficiently use the limited space and meet the daily needs of your store. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/79bb26cc5a2551897b03d4f6fccde66d.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/46459d0bdd783005e91d0273093ec584.avif?t=1746463148\" width=618 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your store with any wallpaper you choose and give it a unique and memorable name. You can also decorate your store however you want!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.poster.avif?t=1746463148\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.webm?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961880/extras/aaa1669868147e05e46e2b0384b0349a.mp4?t=1746463148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
